Battera::

She opened her eyes and looked up at him. Still slightly out of it, 
she hits him with her wing and tries to get free from him. "I'm fine, 
I think." she took a few flaps with her wing, but she didn't have the 
cooridination and started to drop again. "YIPE!"  She fell into a 
tree and landed on the limb. "Ouch. That hurt. Oh my aching pride."
She stood up and transformed into bot mode. She looked up at 
Starscream. "WHoah, where'd you come from?"
